---
import PresentationLayout from '~/layouts/PresentationLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Coding Agents 101: Foundation and Mindset',
  description:
    'An introduction to coding agents and the foundational mindset needed to work effectively with AI-powered development tools.',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: false,
};
---

<PresentationLayout metadata={metadata}>
  <section data-state="title" class="title-slide">
    <h1>Coding Agents 101</h1>
    <h2>Foundation and Mindset</h2>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Agenda</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>AI in Development</li>
      <li>Baseline for achieving great results</li>
      <li>Common Mistakes and Misconceptions</li>
      <li>Best Practices</li>
      <li>Short Demo</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <section>
      <h2>AI in Development</h2>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>Possibilities</h3>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div style="border: 2px solid #0ea5c1; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(14, 165, 193, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🧪</span>
            Test Generation
          </h3>
          <p>Generating Unit, Integration and E2E tests</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #0ea5c1; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(14, 165, 193, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">👁️</span>
            Code Reviews
          </h3>
          <p>Acceptance Criteria, Performance, Guidelines</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #0ea5c1; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(14, 165, 193, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">⚡</span>
            Code Generation
          </h3>
          <p>Code generation at all levels</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #0ea5c1; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(14, 165, 193, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">✨</span>
            And more...
          </h3>
          <p>Documentation, refactoring, bug fixes</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <h3>The Hype</h3>
          <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li>❌ AI builds features autonomously</li>
            <li>❌ AI replaces developers</li>
            <li>❌ 10x productivity overnight</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="fragment">
          <h3>Reality</h3>
          <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li>✅ AI helps <strong>YOU</strong> building features</li>
            <li>✅ AI empowers software engineers</li>
            <li>✅ >2x productivity with proper setup</li>
            <li>✅ >0x if used wrong</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>The "Junior Developer" Mental Model</h2>
      <p>Think of AI as a talented junior developer on your team.</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; margin-top: 2rem; align-items: start;">
        
        <div>
          <h3>Junior devs need:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Good examples to follow</li>
            <li>Clear boundaries</li>
            <li>Code review</li>
            <li>Specific tasks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>AI needs the same:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Strong codebase patterns</li>
            <li>Well-defined scope</li>
            <li>Your oversight</li>
            <li>Focused objectives</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section>
    <section>
      <h2>What can go wrong?</h2>
      <h3>Why integrations fail?</h3>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <div style="border: 2px solid #e8b4b8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(232, 180, 184, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🌪️</span>
            Integrating AI everywhere at once
          </h3>
          <p><strong>Why it fails:</strong> No baseline to measure success, overwhelming to maintain</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #e8b4b8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(232, 180, 184, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🤖</span>
            Generating guidelines with AI
          </h3>
          <p><strong>Why it fails:</strong> AI doesn't understand your context deeply enough</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #e8b4b8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(232, 180, 184, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🏗️</span>
            Big refactoring tasks
          </h3>
          <p><strong>Why it fails:</strong> Too much context, too many decisions, high risk</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #e8b4b8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(232, 180, 184, 0.1);">
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🎯</span>
            Feature one-shot generation
          </h3>
          <p><strong>Why it fails:</strong> Features need iteration, edge cases, business context</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fragment" style="border: 2px solid #f0c36d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(240, 195, 109, 0.15);">
        <p style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin: 0;">
          <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">⚠️</span>
          <strong>The Pattern: Lack of Foundation</strong> — All of these fail because they skip the foundational work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</PresentationLayout>
